OL,3,CJailed shoplifter's 'poor attempt'
OL,4,Cdisguise gets her banned from wearing
OL,5,Cwigs
OL,7,FA woman has been jailed and banned
OL,8,Ffrom wearing wigs in shops after
OL,9,Fcarrying out a string of thefts across
OL,10,FHampshire.
OL,12,FRachael Cole, 44, admitted stealing
OL,13,Falmost #1,000 worth of goods from
OL,14,Fstores in Hook and Liphook during a
OL,15,Fthree-week shoplifting spree in
OL,16,FNovember 2025.
OL,18,FShe appeared at Basingstoke
OL,19,FMagistrates' Court, where she pleaded
OL,20,Fguilty to four counts of theft and was
OL,21,Fsentenced to 36 weeks in prison.
