OL,3,CJailed shoplifter's 'poor attempt'
OL,4,Cdisguise gets her banned from wearing
OL,5,Cwigs
OL,7,FCole, from Whitehill, has also been
OL,8,Fhanded a Criminal Behaviour Order
OL,9,Fwhich bars her from wearing any wig or
OL,10,Fface covering inside a shop.
OL,12,FThe order was imposed after she used a
OL,13,Fwig in an attempt to disguise herself
OL,14,Fwhile stealing seven bags of dog food
OL,15,Ffrom a Sainsbury's store in Liphook.
OL,17,FUnder the order, she is also banned
OL,18,Ffrom every Sainsbury's and Tesco
OL,19,Fnationwide, as well as the B&M store
OL,20,Fin Bordon.
