OL,3,CJailed shoplifter's 'poor attempt'
OL,4,Cdisguise gets her banned from wearing
OL,5,Cwigs
OL,7,FShe must place any items she intends
OL,8,Fto buy in a basket or trolley, show
OL,9,Fshe has the means to pay if asked, and
OL,10,Fleave any shop in Hampshire or Surrey
OL,11,Fwhen requested.
OL,13,FInspector Matt Wake from Hampshire
OL,14,FConstabulary said: "Cole repeatedly
OL,15,Fand brazenly steals from local
OL,16,Fbusinesses, even going as far as to
OL,17,Fmaking a poor attempt at disguising
OL,18,Fherself with a wig to try and deceive
OL,19,Fpolice and shop owners.
